query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.favorite_count >= 0 AND q.favorite_count <= 10000
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('math')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('brownian-motion',
'complex-geometry',
'distribution-theory',
'examples-counterexamples',
'fractions',
'mathematical-physics',
'norm',
'normal-distribution',
'taylor-expansion');
